                  <div id="innerbodycontent" class="row nolayout"><div class="offset1 span10">
            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Comparing "pingshi" and "pingchang"</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=ASGJOGGG&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGJOGGG">ASGJOGGG</a>)</span></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASGJOGGG" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGJOGGG"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="B2_grammar_points" title="B2 grammar points"> B2</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK5_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK5 grammar points">HSK5</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="B2_grammar_points" title="B2 grammar points"> B2</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK5_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK5 grammar points"> HSK5</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Comparing_&quot;changchang&quot;_and_&quot;jingchang&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;changchang&quot; and &quot;jingchang&quot;">Comparing "changchang" and "jingchang"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Comparing_&quot;changchang&quot;_and_&quot;wangwang&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;changchang&quot; and &quot;wangwang&quot;">Comparing "changchang" and "wangwang"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Comparing_&quot;changchang&quot;_and_&quot;wangwang&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;changchang&quot; and &quot;wangwang&quot;">Comparing "changchang" and "wangwang"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK4</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Comparing_&quot;changchang&quot;_and_&quot;jingchang&quot;" title="Comparing &quot;changchang&quot; and &quot;jingchang&quot;">Comparing "changchang" and "jingchang"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK5</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Describing_things" title="Describing things">Describing things</a>, <a href="Referring_to_habitual_actions" title="Referring to habitual actions">Referring to habitual actions</a>, <a href="Expressing_frequency" title="Expressing frequency">Expressing frequency</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="平时" title="平时">平时</a>, <a href="平常" title="平常">平常</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki－平常.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki－平常.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Chinese-grammar-wiki%EF%BC%8D%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%B8.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki%EF%BC%8D%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%B8.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Chinese-grammar-wiki%EF%BC%8D%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%B8.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki%EF%BC%8D%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%B8.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Chinese-grammar-wiki%EF%BC%8D%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%B8.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki%EF%BC%8D%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%B8.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>平时 (píngshí) and 平常 (píngcháng) look very similar (after all, they do start with 平), and they have similar meanings of "often" or "usually," but they have slightly different uses. 
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
